  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## How to compare baselines\n\n1. **Tag your runs** — use `yarn perf:baseline --label <name>` (e.g. `before-sqlite`, `after-sqlite`) or the named shortcuts `yarn perf:baseline:before-sqlite` / `yarn perf:baseline:after-sqlite`\n2. **Set the time range** — expand the picker (top-right) to cover both runs, e.g. *Last 15 days*\n3. **Pick Baseline 1 and Baseline 2** from the dropdowns above — these are the `baseline_label` values passed to k6\n4. **Pick a Profile** — compare like-for-like: `load` vs `load`, `stress` vs `stress`\n5. **Peak row** — shows worst/best instantaneous behavior during each run\n6. **Delta row** — B2 vs B1 summary. For latency/failure cards: negative is better. For throughput: positive is better\n7. **Timeseries** — shape over time for both runs"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "B1 — Peak p95 Latency",
      "description": "Worst p95 HTTP request duration seen across the Baseline 1 run. Lower is better.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "k6_http_req_duration_p95{baseline_label=\"$baseline_label_1\",test_profile=\"$test_profile\"}",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "$baseline_label_1"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 200 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 500 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["max"] },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      }
    },
